#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
#                                     DESCRIPTION
#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
# Z_AliasAllList v0.0.2 :
# List All alias found in ZaemonSH config, therefore they are inactive.

#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
#                                        TODO
#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#

#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
#                                       CHANGES
#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
# 28/09/2017 :
# • Unify script presentation.
